headline: Few companies survive three decades on the internet, let alone thrive – buy
summary: When the Iranian-American entrepreneur, Pierre Omidyar, founded eBay in his living room in 1995, he took one of the most established ways of conducting commerce and adapted it for a burgeoning technological age.
